        public void update(java.lang.String key,

        Updates each option value according to parsed result of command response.

        (CAUTION) Some setting options won't be updated even though successful sending command. - FREQUENCY: get un-proper result to extract updated value - WIFI: (TODO) don't know how to test about it - PROTOCOL: get un-proper result to extract updated value

        Parameters:
        key - command header
        response - response of command
